race.comment: SUNTORA (6) is racing well, just missing Sun Gift two back at Cranbourne who went on to beat TRAPALANDA. She was solid to the line last time when back in trip and should be suited up in trip again now. STEEL RUN (7) resumes. He didn't quite fire in three runs last time in but has staying ability and can be hitting the line strongly. STYLISH SECRET (5) wasn't far away behind Sun Gift last time and could sneak into the placings while OPENING ADDRESS (4) maps well and has minor claims on best form. ACTIVE DUTY (9) was much better second-up when sticking on gamely into fourth. Peaking now and can make his presence felt.
